HEADWORD: Stewardess
<hw>Stew"ard*ess</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A female steward;
specifically, a woman employed in passenger vessels to attend to the
wants of female passengers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

